room_title: Escape room "The Voodoo Cabin" by Gulf Coast Escape Room in Orange Beach
room_address: 701 Gulf Shores Parkway Gulf Shores, AL 36542
room_description: You have gone to New Orleans to party for Mardi Gra and you get drugged and kidnapped. When you wake up, you and several other friends find yourselves trapped in the Marie Laveau Voodoo Cabin. You have an hour to escape the cabin before you are sacrificed!
